name: DateAndTime_betweenTest
description: Unit tests for the DateAndTime class's between method.

test_cases.name: testBetweenValidRange
test_cases.description: Tests the between method with a valid range, ensuring the result is within the specified timestamps.

test_cases.name: testBetweenEqualDates
test_cases.description: Tests the between method with equal timestamps, ensuring the result is the same as the input timestamps.

test_cases.name: testBetweenInvalidRange
test_cases.description: Tests the between method with an invalid range, ensuring an IllegalArgumentException is thrown.
